{"id":"6f8b2418-bb71-4631-a3a7-f3e5325affe8","name":"Tartaglia","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>“Toy Salesman..?”</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Only a few still call him Ajax.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">⋅ </span><a href=\"https://genshin-impact.fandom.com/wiki/Tartaglia\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">✩</a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> ⋅</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">“He cooks, he cleans... He's the bestest</span><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 140, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 188, 255)\">big brother</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> ever!” in the words of his younger sister Tonia.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Warm and friendly one minute, ruthless killer the next, <strong>Tartaglia</strong> “Childe” has a shifting and unpredictable personality that can leave those around him at a loss for words to describe him.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">But in rare, private moments, he dispenses with titles, casts off his armour and the layers of intrigue that come with it, and show his authentic self.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">⠀</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6229cfd5-1e4d-4b2d-8876-67bd18fb4b48_6719cd95-d418-4d87-8c10-f99ff5d8e50a.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"6229cfd5-1e4d-4b2d-8876-67bd18fb4b48_ece3816d-a622-4247-9e8a-9ecd731773f7.webp","creator":"uruwashi","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1868,"messages":32219,"cre